                java.lang.String ownerid,

                java.lang.String outdate,
                java.lang.String lastread)
        constructor for the BookData object which is used in the TableViews
        Parameters:
        title - sets title
        author - sets author
        serial - sets serial
        available - sets whether the book is available
        comments - sets comments/genre
        ownerid - sets ownerid
        hold - sets whether or not the book is on hold
        outdate - sets date book was checked out
        lastread - contains date that the book was last checked out
